  <h3>Other Ways You Can Help Pets</h3>
  <p><strong>Post, Tweet, and Share Pets Available for  Adoption</strong><br>
    A great way  to help pets find homes is simply by talking about them. Find a local pet  adoption organization near you and share pets looking for homes on Facebook,  Twitter or Instagram. Be sure to include a link to the pet adoption  organization&rsquo;s website!</p>
  <p><strong>Volunteer or Fundraise at Your Local Pet  Adoption Organization</strong><br>
    You don&rsquo;t  need to know the ins and outs of animal behavior to help a pet adoption  organization. Many orgs need help in the following areas: office tasks, answering  the phone, taking photos/videos of adoptable pets, or simply directing guests  who come in looking for pet adoption. Reach out to your local org today!</p>
